# Privacy Policy for Adv.ServiceCenter

**Last Updated**: April 24, 2026

## Data Collection

**Adv.ServiceCenter does not collect, transmit, or store any telemetry, analytics, or personal data.**

All processing occurs locally within your YouTrack instance.

## External Services

**The app does not contact any external services.** All form processing, issue creation, and configuration management are performed entirely within the YouTrack app runtime.

## Data Processing

- The app renders forms and creates YouTrack issues based on user input and administrator configuration
- Form definitions and settings are stored in YouTrack app settings and extension properties
- No form data, user data, or credentials are logged or transmitted to third parties

## Contact

For privacy-related questions, contact: apps@mag1.cc
